00287 static XED_INLINE xed_uint_t
00288 xed_decoded_inst_get_machine_mode_bits(const xed_decoded_inst_t* p) {
00289     xed_uint8_t mode = xed3_operand_get_mode(p);
00290     if (mode == 2) return 64;
00291     if (mode == 1) return 32;
00292     return 16;
00293 }
00297 static XED_INLINE xed_uint_t
00298 xed_decoded_inst_get_stack_address_mode_bits(const xed_decoded_inst_t* p) {
00299     xed_uint8_t smode = xed3_operand_get_smode(p);
00300     if (smode == 2) return 64;
00301     if (smode == 1) return 32;
00302     return 16;
00303 }
